'''''A United Kingdom''''' ni romantic drama film yasohotse muri 2016 muri [[Botswana]] iyoborwa na Amma Asante yanditswe na Guy Hibbert<ref>https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/a_united_kingdom</ref>, ishingiye ku urugo nyakuri, ubuzima hagati ya Seretse Khama<ref>https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/a-united-kingdom-2017</ref>, kuragwa ubutegetsi kwa Bechuanaland ( yari perezida wa [[Botswana]])<ref>https://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/nov/27/a-united-kingdom-review-love-story-amma-asante-david-oyelowo-rosamund-pike</ref>,  n'umugore we Ruth Williams Khama .  David Oyelowo na Rosamund Pike bagaragaza Seretse na Ruth<ref>https://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/sep/09/a-united-kingdom-review-rosamund-pike-david-oyelowo-toronto</ref>.

Yerekanwe mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Toronto mu 2016<ref>https://www.allocine.fr/film/fichefilm_gen_cfilm=237771.html</ref>,  kandi ni yo filime yatangiye iserukiramuco rya sinema rya 60 rya London.<ref>https://www.npr.org/2017/02/24/517029375/david-oyelowo-on-the-real-united-kingdom-marriage-and-its-diplomatic-fallout</ref> 

