== uko yakozwe ==
Pike yinjiye mu bakinnyi muri Gicurasi 2015, Asante yinjira nyuma gato<ref>https://www.intofilm.org/news-and-views/articles/a-united-kingdom-feature</ref>.  Muri Nzeri 2015, Asante yatangaje ko gufata amashusho bizagabanywa hagati ya [[Botswana]] na London<ref>https://www.ft.com/content/937c7a78-b23a-11e6-9c37-5787335499a0</ref>, kandi ko bizatangira mu Kwakira mu rwego rwo kwitegura irekurwa rya filimi muri 2016 rihurirana n’imyaka 50 y'ubwigenge muri [[Botswana]]<ref>https://variety.com/2016/film/reviews/a-united-kingdom-review-1201856430/</ref>.  Mu Kwakira 2015, Jack Davenport na Tom Felton bifatanije n'aba bakinnyi<ref>https://www.bbc.co.uk/bbcfilm/films/a-united-kingdom/</ref>.  Mu Gushyingo 2015, amashusho amwe yabereye hafi ya Hyde Park / Kensington Gardens harimo na Imperial College Union<ref>http://www.simonbowles.com/auk</ref> . Umukinnyi wa sinema yari Sam McCurdy naho umuyobozi wa filimi  yari Simon Bowles<ref>https://raisingchildren.net.au/guides/movie-reviews/united-kingdom-a</ref> 

